  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>There's a good breakfast here with plenty of choices including hot options.</p>
<p>Lunch snacks are served on the sun terrace (payable locally)</p>
<p>You'll get a three-course dinner each evening, including a self-service salad buffet.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
