  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Astoria promises friendly Italian hospitality in a great location. Whatever the weather, the hotel's bar and lounge have all you need for exchanging ski stories with friends and a well-earned drink in hand.</p>
<h2>Location</h2>
<p>The Plan Maison cable car is only 50 metres away, which is great for getting straight on the slopes and even better when you get back after a long day of skiing or boarding.</p>
<h2>Rooftop Sauna</h2>
<p>Head up to the roof to take a dip in the hotel's plunge pool, or warm up in the sauna. You will have incredible views of the Matterhorn while you relax.</p>
<h2>Dining</h2>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/bfccaf52eb4c47f09ae3657298234fda" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bfccaf52eb4c47f09ae3657298234fda}" title="Cervinia">Cervinia's</a> centre is just a few minutes' walk away and there's plenty of shops, bars and restaurants to discover here. When it comes to your evening meal, the Astoria restaurant has you sorted.</p>
<p>The food is delicious and the portions are just right. Try and grab a seat with amazing views of the mountains - you can even see the Matterhorn from some of the rooms.</p>
<p>Bluebird days make the hotel's sun terrace a great place to chill in the afternoon.</p>]]></description>
